    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that house privately run schools with programs organized as an alternative to traditional public or private schools, usually with a highly flexible or voluntaristic framework.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
